  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This research will be a prospective single-centre observational cohort study in Aarhus,&#xD;
      Denmark spanning approximately one year. The objective of this study is to develop a&#xD;
      clinically applicable and generalizable prediction model for CPSP in adults.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
